 2023-07112023-06-30PSPC
ActNational Capital Act
SubjectOrder Approving that the NCC Extend the Lease with Rideau Sports Centre Inc.
PrecisOrder approving that the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION grant one option to extend the lease with RIDEAU SPORTS CENTRE INC. for real property located at 1 Donald Street, in Ottawa, Ontario, for a period of nineteen years, beginning on March 1, 2034.
